=====Usage note=====
* [[两]] is used when counting things with a measure word, [[二]] is used in numbers. 
* Examples with [[两]]
*: 两个人 two people, 两年 two years
* Examples with [[二]]
*: [[二十]] twenty (literally "two tens"), [[第二]] second

